{"tid":2498550,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨2021暑期實習計劃，你問我答","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T10:13:40.000Z","uid":250449,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc92a6632a1663cc912281bc641e251581e2448","tid":2498550,"uid":250449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"民主黨2021仲搞實習呀？！！！<br />\n原來真係搞，仲有OCAMP添！！CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【民主黨2021暑期實習計劃正式接受報名】</strong><br />\n人生流流長，有幾可會在政黨內工作？與我們一起成長的實習生們，都會有很獨特、難忘的經驗，幸運的話也會建立到經年累月的友誼喔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民主青年實習計劃現正招生，有意報名的大家請留意相關細節！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lucky.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實習期：    5月24日至7月16日(為期8星期)<br />\n實習時數：150小時<br />\n實習津貼：每小時$40及實習期滿津貼$1500<br />\n面試日期：5月10-14日<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">迎新營</span></span>： 5月22日至23日(星期六, 日) <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">報名連結：  <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3uFlzJT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3uFlzJT&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ae55b4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3uFlzJT</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n截止報名日期: 5月5日(星期五) 下午6點正"},{"pid":"69afbf626d1e3fec65b1454d4666293886c4af26","tid":2498550,"uid":367101,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"羅健熙幾時投共呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764bdbabc457e6e8b71d8f401aa8b20ad41caef5","tid":2498550,"uid":213656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"這討論區有管理員嗎？"},{"pid":"3079a6602a2acebc79ab8bff9f0c90cba84e6cf8","tid":2498550,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"議助你近排有工開嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" clas